summary: A group of models and textures for your use. Happy Halloween !
descriptionHtml:
This is 25 models with textures for Halloween that you can use in your mods.
I have them set up in a small farm mod so you can see them in game, west of Morthal.
THIS IS A MODDERS RESOURCE !

Includes...
3 new gravestones
2 candlesticks
2 lit pumpkins
2 different eyeballs
3 floating heads, 2 are skulls,1 is a pumpkin
4 statues, scarecrow,death angel, evil clown, pile of skulls
1 trick or treat bag
1 pumpkin bucket
1 animated perched Raven
1 butcher knife
1 butcher cleaver
1 chainsaw
1 animated bubbling cauldron
1 skull candle with flame
1 necronomicon book

I hope you enjoy these and use them. Please credit me for my work and do not upload this file anywhere else. Thanks, BadGremlin

If you use these post your pics !
author: BadGremlin
